    "body": "This PR adds a feature to `FieldTimeSeries` that allows us to load data which is distributed across multiple files by `file_splitting`.\r\n\r\nI regard this implementation as a prototype; hopefully we can improve it in the future and also extend support to other backends like `OnDisk`. In particular I think `set!` can possibly be improved.\r\n\r\nFeedback welcome. I think @ali-ramadhan and @josuemtzmo would be interested in this. I also need to add a test; any help with that is very appreciated!",
